archimate:BusinessObject.name: EIRA View
archimate:BusinessObject.documentation:
The EIRA© consists of several architecture views(1), including one view for each of the EIF interoperability levels. The EIRA© views contain a graphical notation of the EIRA© ontology.
(1) An architecture view is a representation of a system from the perspective of a related set of concerns. Source: TOGAF https://pubs.opengroup.org/architecture/togaf9-doc/arch/chap03.html#tag_03_17
